Basic Plot¶

In [3]:
spread = alt.Chart(df).mark_area(opacity=0.3).encode(
    x=alt.X('Date', timeUnit='year'),
    y=alt.Y('ci0(BOPD)', axis=alt.Axis(title='BOPD')),
    y2='ci1(BOPD)',
    color='Well_Name'
).properties(
    title='Volve Field Production',
    width=800
)
lines = alt.Chart(df).mark_line().encode(
    x=alt.X('Date', timeUnit='year'),
    y='mean(BOPD)',
    color='Well_Name'
).properties(
    width=800
)
spread + lines

Map with interactivity from Map on Production and BHP data¶

2 maps to show interactivity¶

In [4]:
interval = alt.selection_interval()
base = alt.Chart(df).mark_circle().encode(
    x='XX_Bottom', 
    #scale=alt.Scale(zero=False)),
    #size='BOPD',
    size=alt.Size('BOPD:Q', scale=alt.Scale(range=[10, 1000])),
    
    #label='Well_Name',
    color=alt.condition(interval, 'Well_Name', alt.value('lightgray')),
    tooltip='Well_Name', 
).properties(
    title='Volve Field Map Showing Producing Wells',
    selection=interval
)



text = base.mark_text(align='left', dx=5, dy=-5).encode(
text='Well_Name'
)




bhp = alt.Chart(df).mark_circle().encode(
    x='Date',
    y='BHP',
    color='Well_Name:O'
    #color='BOPD:Q'
).properties(
    title='Volve Field - BHP',
    width=800,
    height=180,
    selection=interval
).transform_filter(
    interval
)



hist = alt.Chart(df).mark_bar().encode(
    x='Date',
    y='BOPD',
    color='Well_Name'
).properties(
    title='Volve Field - Oil Production',
    width=800,
    height=180,
    #selection=interval
).transform_filter(
    interval
)

hist2 = alt.Chart(df).mark_bar().encode(
    x='Date',
    y='BWPD',
    color='Well_Name:O'
    #color='BOPD:Q'
).properties(
    title='Volve Field - Water Production',
    width=800,
    height=180,
    #selection=interval
).transform_filter(
    interval
)



scatter = base.encode(y='YY_Bottom') | base.encode(y='YY_Bottom',size='BWPD:Q')
#scatter = base.encode(y='YY_Bottom',size=alt.Size('BOPD:Q')) | base.encode(y='YY_Bottom',size=alt.Size('BWPD:Q'))
#scatter = base.encode(y='YY_Bottom')

interval = alt.selection_interval()
base = alt.Chart(df).mark_circle().encode(
    x='XX_Bottom', 
    #scale=alt.Scale(zero=False)),
    #size='BOPD',
    size=alt.Size('BOPD:Q', scale=alt.Scale(range=[10, 1000])),
    
    #label='Well_Name',
    color=alt.condition(interval, 'Well_Name', alt.value('lightgray')),
    tooltip='Well_Name', 
).properties(
    title='Volve Field Map Showing Producing Wells Sized by BPOD or BWPD',
    selection=interval
)

text = base.mark_text(
    align='center',
    baseline='middle',
    dx=7
).encode(
    text='Well_Name'
)

bhp = alt.Chart(df).mark_circle().encode(
    x='Date',
    y='BHP',
    color='Well_Name:O'
    #color='BOPD:Q'
).properties(
    title='Volve Field - BHP',
    width=800,
    height=180,
    selection=interval
)



hist = alt.Chart(df).mark_bar().encode(
    x='Date',
    y='BOPD',
    color='Well_Name'
).properties(
    title='Volve Field - Oil Production',
    width=800,
    height=180,
    selection=interval

)

hist2 = alt.Chart(df).mark_bar().encode(
    x='Date',
    y='BWPD',
    color='Well_Name:O'
    #color='BOPD:Q'
).properties(
    title='Volve Field - Water Production',
    width=800,
    height=180,
    selection=interval

)

In [7]:
interval = alt.selection_interval()

base = alt.Chart(df).properties(
    width=350,
    height=350, 
).add_selection(interval)


points = base.mark_point(filled=True, size=200).encode(
    x='XX_Bottom:Q',
    y='YY_Bottom:Q',
    size='BOPD:Q',
    color=alt.condition(interval, 'Well_Name', alt.value('lightgray')),
    #color=alt.condition(selector, 'Well_Name:O', alt.value('lightgray'), legend=None),
    tooltip='Well_Name', 
).properties(
    title='Volve Field Map',
    selection=interval
)


timeseries = base.mark_line().encode(
    x='Date',
    y=alt.Y('BOPD', scale=alt.Scale(domain=(0, 40000))),
    color=alt.Color('Well_Name:O')
    
).properties(
    title='Volve Production by Well in BOPD',
    width=350,
    height=140
    #selection=interval
).transform_filter(
    #title='Volve Field BOPD',    
    interval
)


timeseries2 = base.mark_line().encode(
    x='Date',
    y=alt.Y('BWPD', scale=alt.Scale(domain=(0, 40000))),
    color=alt.Color('Well_Name:O')
    
).properties(
    title='Volve Production by Well in BWPD',
    width=350,
    height=140
    #selection=interval
).transform_filter(
    #title='Volve Field BOPD',    
    interval
)



bhp = alt.Chart(df).mark_circle().encode(
    x='Date',
    y='BHP',
    color='Well_Name:O'
    #color='BOPD:Q'
).properties(
    title='Volve Field - BHP',
    width=700,
    height=180,
    selection=interval
).transform_filter(
    interval
)


hist = alt.Chart(df).mark_bar().encode(
    #x='count()',
    x='sum(BOPM)',
    y='Well_Name',
    color='Well_Name'
).properties(
    width=700,
    height=80
).transform_filter(
    interval
)

hist2 = alt.Chart(df).mark_bar().encode(
    #x='count()',
    x='sum(BWPM)',
    y='Well_Name',
    color='Well_Name'
).properties(
    width=700,
    height=80
).transform_filter(
    interval
)

hist3 = alt.Chart(df).mark_bar().encode(
    x='sum(beGpm)',
    y='Well_Name',
    color='Well_Name'
).properties(
    width=700,
    height=80
).transform_filter(
    interval
)

first = points | timeseries & timeseries2 
second = bhp & hist & hist2 & hist3

interval = alt.selection_interval()

base = alt.Chart(df).properties(
    width=300,
    height=300, 
).add_selection(interval)

points = base.mark_point(filled=True, size=200).encode(
    x='XX_Bottom:Q',
    y='YY_Bottom:Q',
    size='BOPD:Q',
    color=alt.condition(interval, 'Well_Name', alt.value('lightgray')),
    #color=alt.condition(selector, 'Well_Name:O', alt.value('lightgray'), legend=None),
    tooltip='Well_Name', 
).properties(
    title='Volve Field Map',
    selection=interval


)

timeseries = base.mark_line().encode(
    x='Date',
    y=alt.Y('Cum_Oil', scale=alt.Scale(domain=(0, 30000000))),
    color=alt.Color('Well_Name:O')
    
).properties(
    title='Volve Cum_Oil by Well',
    #selection=interval


).transform_filter(
    #title='Volve Field BOPD',    
    interval
)

timeseries2 = base.mark_line().encode(
    x='Date',
    y=alt.Y('Cum_Water', scale=alt.Scale(domain=(0, 50000000))),
    color=alt.Color('Well_Name:O')
    
).properties(
    title='Volve Cum_Water by Well',
    #selection=interval


).transform_filter(
    #title='Volve Field BOPD',    
    interval
)

timeseries3 = base.mark_line().encode(
    x='Cum_Water',
    y=alt.Y('Cum_Oil', scale=alt.Scale(domain=(0, 30000000))),
    color=alt.Color('Well_Name:O')
    
).properties(
    title='Volve Cum_Oil and Cum_Water by Well',
    #selection=interval


).transform_filter(
    #title='Volve Field BOPD',    
    interval
)


first = points | timeseries
second = timeseries2 | timeseries3


#points & timeseries & timeseries2 & timeseries3
